{"tid":1616084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十一黃大仙 一名街坊的感謝","createTime":"2019-10-03T09:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T16:10:05.000Z","uid":74084,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a70b12d43ead1eaf441647d2cc6fda69442ed05","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"前日見假期諗住去行下獅子山<br />\n點知行到沙田坳道幼稚園對出<br />\n無啦啦吹陣怪風埋黎<br />\n成條街街坊都唔舒服跑走<br />\n跑到橫街一半見街尾班街坊都開始向上跑<br />\n成條街鋪頭都落哂閘<br />\n心諗金翅仆街鳥之際<br />\n<br />\n突然有間鋪開咗半閘仲係咁叫我地快d入去於是我就同超過廿個街坊入左去<br />\n見到好多都好細個好驚<br />\n有個弟弟個樣睇落成個小學生咁<br />\n老闆係咁𥄫實叫佢坐低涼冷氣驚佢自己一個又走返出去<br />\n有其他人問老闆知唔知個弟弟幾歲<br />\n老闆好似有d眼濕濕咁話唔敢問<br />\n後來先知個弟弟得14歲...<br />\n聽完大家心情都有d沉重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一輪梳洗同休息後大家都陸續離開<br />\n走前本身想同老闆你相認道謝<br />\n點知未出聲你就大大力拍我膊頭兩下<br />\n同我講萬事小心煲底見<br />\n今次到我眼濕濕 點左下頭就走左<br />\n<br />\n點解我會話相認道謝<br />\n其實係因為之前已經嚟過你鋪頭好幾次<br />\n雖然我成日都無幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但聽你講過話附近街坊都深藍<br />\n見你唔開又問你係咪罷工<br />\n又話暴動唔敢落嚟你鋪頭 冷嘲熱諷<br />\n前日一路跑一路見d鋪落哂閘<br />\n我真係無諗過會係咁既情況下入到你鋪頭<br />\n<br />\n知你有上連登 唔知你會唔會見到<br />\n老闆 多謝你 一路以來辛苦你<br />\n唔知你會唔會唔想高調 名我唔開啦<br />\n但我希望其他廿幾位街坊<br />\n可以的話叫親戚朋友去幫襯下老闆<br />\n滴水之恩 當湧泉相報<br />\n煲底見"},{"pid":"edbff1ff0283b2b72e2f3058cd2fc8ad0e0f846e","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"推到其餘廿幾個街坊見到"},{"pid":"f2f64b5c1d53c9a5e54ff687c482dd163446e850","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:52:52.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"9480bd13f39cc52bcce2e08b04a3933d576afd66","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbc857954f3b2d575fbe65af7077f828b0d0b08e","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"再輕輕一推"},{"pid":"dbf64ccc7322d985038d0f70493fe837ca54896c","tid":1616084,"uid":183308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:10:58.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"88668b14f090ba8159f001a91337b20d89e7b13f","tid":1616084,"uid":8589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"邊間 一定落去幫襯佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係住果頭"},{"pid":"72334de6c548ad85571faf64c55702dbff372a6d","tid":1616084,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:14:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"242e9aef55f8e0d47af4fc6e6166e93fb8810964","tid":1616084,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"推 個夢好真實"},{"pid":"826deeabf44d12ac66b2fc9ced9130630dd2ac5e","tid":1616084,"uid":216481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以加密講下係邊間 想支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3158ca5b38b7e2ae5279018dad0dc7a59698a442","tid":1616084,"uid":104957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7311fdb04f24bf43d58bb4aa22db9129d9a1bc96","tid":1616084,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n患難見真情"},{"pid":"1ef75751c24d3b61144d6d4f3344c140378ab6e9","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88668b14f090ba8159f001a91337b20d89e7b13f","tid":1616084,"uid":8589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"邊間 一定落去幫襯佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係住果頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"唔敢開名呀 驚害到老闆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c6a05ecd