之前聽佢講街坊同鋪頭已經好深感受<br />\n原來自己射一日波扣一千幾百勤工就做到既事<br />\n有d人要受咁大壓力先做到<br />\n然而仍然咁撐咁支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6ec3c2e59ffde7659bb3ec3f6aa7bbe78378ad","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c6a05ecd6fa9fc8cab3861fec5f8107fc03f8b","tid":1616084,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"826deeabf44d12ac66b2fc9ced9130630dd2ac5e","tid":1616084,"uid":216481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以加密講下係邊間 想支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:18:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主唔好理佢</strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"知道 多謝手足提醒<br />\n希望當日其他街坊盡自己能力私了懲罰老闆"},{"pid":"fb6d804edb7f9df6751042cb47e0cde67192091a","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09c09884188224de943fd9d91ba06ac8af188f0c","tid":1616084,"uid":90743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1ef75751c24d3b61144d6d4f3344c140378ab6e9","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88668b14f090ba8159f001a91337b20d89e7b13f","tid":1616084,"uid":8589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"邊間 一定落去幫襯佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係住果頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"唔敢開名呀 驚害到老闆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"唔好講太多啦 危險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"知道 <br />\n真係好心酸又無可奈何<br />\n好似連少少野都報答唔到咁<br />\n老闆 多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6933fe1ab446bf7766558ceee77b659205d92a","tid":1616084,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c8b6b659add9520a27dd714891e6e672f5d08ab","tid":1616084,"uid":196964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0efd40c575c980c616d95935f5dca4e2a85443e","tid":1616084,"uid":106051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:52:31.000Z","msg":"一定咪開名<br />\n一陣下場變國難"},{"pid":"4fc869961da3432cd0eaff13bb27ed24d2550777","tid":1616084,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52fc631738218d94905d8c5ebcbab013d39e247e","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0efd40c575c980c616d95935f5dca4e2a85443e","tid":1616084,"uid":106051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:52:31.000Z","msg":"一定咪開名<br />\n一陣下場變國難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"放心一定唔會<br />\n見深水埗甜一刻出事已經知一定唔可以開名<br />\n純粹想睇下有無方法可以報答返老闆"},{"pid":"2c648c64cbb723458a0ea80afb1c0f83997ed153","tid":1616084,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:46:53.000Z","msg":"追左陣post見有幾個黃店報料<br />\n想問下有無話邊個信得過/實際d?<br />\n<br />\n另外想講 當日應該好多街坊都有上連登<br />\n我懇求你哋用自己方法去懲罰返老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一人介紹一個親戚朋友已經多30個客<br />\n就算無都入黎講返聲多謝<br />\n希望老闆會睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}